T.query: select e.emp_no  as emp_no ,salary,first_name,last_name,birth_date,hire_date,from_date  from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no where e.emp_no > 20000 and s.from_date > '1990-01-01' and e.last_name like 'Al%' and e.gender = 'M' and e.birth_date > '1960-01-01' and s.salary > 80000;
